{"tid":1516944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］被包圍的解決方法","createTime":"2019-08-29T17:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T18:01:40.000Z","uid":170199,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"610cb5e182deaba5a5091c2ba78b5076f75b2bb6","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"見到深水埗今晚咁<br />\n<br />\n俾狗咬 掙扎只會令黑警攞正牌打多兩錢重<br />\n<br />\n應該一俾狗咬 學機場兩件公安 大叫警察打人 之後扮暈 又或者知道走唔甩 俾包圍 就率先暈低係街頭<br />\n<br />\n一來俾自己冷靜 唔好講錯野<br />\n<br />\n二來暈左仲要查身份證或者使用武力 咁佢地就大獲啦<br />\n<br />\n如果黑警唔call 白車 佢地就係見死不救 阻止救援 <br />\n<br />\n同埋突然暈低 起翻身都可能會輕微失憶 又點會知暈之前做緊咩"},{"pid":"4541b3e9f5a1044b1381a925c7e4fc4b747c45b3","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b32b00515d58a62f609af4a512de6afc433f2e35","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:54:42.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"0fa6a0d8559f09987296d66fac25048bbb7dc0c0","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:54:54.000Z","msg":"7.21"},{"pid":"6fe4f65e03ddcebd2415c94796a79b4947065fe8","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24a8350c7eb59bcf753c13c9a80b7a76a9a16171","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d2ac5d052a1855baa270818ae328db38f30e75c","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b78f2c520db90200007100fb8665f6db8b61526","tid":1516944,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:59:24.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5a771f224c64c1d8cf987b981bff129bc7687261","tid":1516944,"uid":295639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"狗最鐘意立背